  <static seed="2565" source="Contrib/PCC/BasicAlgebra/Exponents/exponentsMultiplication0.pg">
    <statement><p>Use the properties of exponents to simplify the expression.</p>
<p><m>{x^{2}}\cdot{x^{8}}</m></p>
<p><fillin characters="12" name="AnSwEr0001"/></p>
</statement>
    <answer>
      <p>
        <m>x^{10}</m>
      </p>
    </answer>
    <solution><p>We <em>add</em> the exponents as follows: <me>\begin{aligned}
           x^{2}\cdot x^{8}\amp =x^{2+8}\\
                             \amp =x^{10}
       \end{aligned}</me></p>
</solution>
